{"tid":745420,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"有樣野想大家幫幫手","createTime":"2018-07-16T17:45:08.000Z","updateTime":"2018-07-16T18:44:54.000Z","uid":17360,"like":2,"dislike":16,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"0253f281ed6bb4c39ffc55ddf0f2c39779fb2727","tid":745420,"uid":17360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T17:45:08.000Z","msg":"話說我14號去咗蘭桂坊飲野<br />\n結果不勝酒力 醉倒路旁<br />\n係半醉半醒既時間<br />\n有兩個女仔行埋黎問我有無事<br />\n但係我已經唔記得我答咗啲咩<br />\n我想親口同你講聲多謝<br />\n事關我班friend 已經走撚曬<br />\n我仲瞓係個度<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n我依稀記得你中短髮 黑色衫<br />\n你個friend 白色tee 長髮<br />\n大大聲笑鳩我個個<br />\n<br />\n各位巴絲如果14號晚有去到<br />\n或者 你有朋友14號晚有去玩<br />\n懇求你地幫下手<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0f6f6efe818dbdcfd08df60acc2c0b75f3417d44","tid":745420,"uid":17360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T17:55:54.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"03fc7d48a905f6d503caa47dff353cb3bd5c781d","tid":745420,"uid":17360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T17:57:18.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"8822557b504807cb2646b1a3ff87ee2b3014b580","tid":745420,"uid":17360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T17:59:21.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a16949f61f87161c08f571c0149374631598242d","tid":745420,"uid":17360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T18:03:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f84893dbad9611dfabec9c3e8df967679f8b6cd0","tid":745420,"uid":17360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T18:04:05.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"4fb16f3165fb25166294acc648898549fd7d6a6f","tid":745420,"uid":17360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T18:04:15.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"6c2274cbed335d9ba6d18c8abb9f260d0dc04dcc","tid":745420,"uid":17360,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-07-16T18:04:26.000Z","msg":"